703851f-a.title: Brooklyn: Court Street - Congress Street
703851f-a.text:
Court Street, at the S.W. corner of Congress Street. This is a rear view of the St. Paul's R.C. Church, as seen from Congress Street.
August 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
